  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nA before-and-after study in Western Australia\u00a0found that a combination of cutting followed by glyphosate chemical treatment, removed floating pennywort."
}

{
  "action_id": "1126",
  "action_title": "Floating pennywort: Physical removal",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nA study in Western Australia\u00a0found that following a two-week program of physical removal of floating pennywort, the rate of growth exceeded the rate of removal.\nA study in the UK, found that removal using a mechanical digger and monthly picking by hand greatly reduced the cover of floating pennywort but did not completely eradicate it."
}

{
  "action_id": "1129",
  "action_title": "Floating pennywort: Use of hydrogen peroxide",
  "key_messages": "Key Messages:\n\nA controlled, replicated pilot study in The Netherlands, found that hydrogen peroxide sprayed on potted floating pennywort plants resulted in curling and transparency of the leaves when applied at the highest tested concentration (30%), but this was still not sufficient to kill the plant."
}

